<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>netstandard2.0;net452</TargetFrameworks>
    <Description>A cross platform C# library for the Ledger hardware wallet. 

To see the sample in a .NET Core unit test, please clone the repo. https://github.com/MelbourneDeveloper/Ledger.Net
 . Android, and UWP samples on their way.

